               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17930410-13-cd73" type="crimeDate">28th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-13-off72 t17930410-13-cd73"></join>, a wooden hamper, value 2 s. and ninety five pounds weight of spun cotton value 7 l.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17930410-13-victim173" type="victimName">
                     Daniel 
                     Mason
                  <interp inst="t17930410-13-victim173" type="surname" value="Mason"></interp>
